1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Your Monday brain fog
starts on Saturday morning.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Every Monday you're sluggish, unfocused, slow. You
blame the alarm. Or the meeting.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
But the damage happened 48 hours earlier when
you slept 3 hours later than usual.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
This Saturday: set an alarm 90 minutes after your weekday
time. Get up. Get light. Watch what Monday feels like.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:30,000
I built an app that tracks
this for you. 30 seconds. Free.

